    <h1>GDPR (General Data Protection Regulation)</h1>
    <p class="description">The EU privacy law enacted in 2018 that governs how organisations collect, process, and store personal data. Applies to any company with EU customers — maximum fines reach <strong>20 million euros or 4% of global annual revenue</strong>, and EU regulators have issued over 4.5 billion euros in penalties since implementation.</p>
