            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Maximum fines are 20 million euros or 4% of global annual revenue, whichever is higher. EU regulators have issued over 4.5 billion euros in total fines since 2018. Meta received a single 1.2 billion euro fine for unauthorised data transfers.</p></div></div>
          </div>
