              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes, if your website uses non-essential cookies (analytics, advertising, personalisation) for EU visitors. Essential cookies enabling site function do not require consent. The banner must give users a genuine choice to accept or decline.</p></div></div>
